OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1773668268
OL,3,CLondoners could be charged for driving
OL,4,CSUVs in the capital
OL,6,FThe Mayor of London Sir Sadiq Khan is
OL,7,Fconsidering charging large SUVs to
OL,8,Fdrive in the capital.
OL,10,FThe proposal is part of Transport for
OL,11,FLondon's Vision Zero action plan which
OL,12,Fwarned that there is a "pressing need
OL,13,Ffor targeted safety interventions"
OL,14,Fover larger vehicles.
OL,16,FThe Vision Zero document said the size
OL,17,Fof large SUVs "significantly increase
OL,18,Fthe severity of collisions" and make
OL,19,Froads "more hazardous for everybody
OL,20,Foutside the vehicle".
OL,26,@tD@XOUuD@bO]{D@GOU|D@TO]
