OL,3,CLondoners could be charged for driving
OL,4,CSUVs in the capital
OL,6,FThe plan is part of Sir Sadiq's
OL,7,Fefforts to eliminate deaths and
OL,8,Fserious injuries on London's roads by
OL,9,F2041.
OL,11,FSUVs is a term given to vehicles that
OL,12,Fare generally taller, wider and
OL,13,Fheavier than traditional cars, and
OL,14,Fless fuel efficient.
OL,16,FThey have grown in popularity in
OL,17,Frecent years, and account for around a
OL,18,Fthird of all new car registrations in
OL,19,Fthe UK.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
