OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1773668268
OL,3,CLondoners could be charged for driving
OL,4,CSUVs in the capital
OL,6,FThe Vision Zero document claimed that
OL,7,Ftheir large size makes it "harder for
OL,8,Fdrivers to see people walking and
OL,9,Fcycling nearby".
OL,11,FIt stated that in Britain, SUVs are
OL,12,F77% more likely to kill children than
OL,13,Fother cars if involved in a collision.
OL,14,FIt also said they are 14% more likely
OL,15,Fto kill pedestrians and cyclists.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the mayor said:
OL,18,F"There is growing evidence about the
OL,19,Fsafety risks of large SUVs, which are
OL,21,Fbecoming more common on London's roads.
OL,26,@oD@[OUqD@OO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
