OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1773668268
OL,3,CLondoners could be charged for driving
OL,4,CSUVs in the capital
OL,6,F"It's a startling figure that SUVs are
OL,7,F77% more likely to kill a child if
OL,8,Finvolved in a collision.
OL,10,F"The mayor has asked TfL to undertake
OL,11,Fdetailed analysis of the safety risks
OL,12,Fposed by large SUVs and their wider
OL,13,Fimpact on London's roads.
OL,15,F"This could then inform any future
OL,16,Fpolicy proposals in London or
OL,17,Frecommendations to Government or the
OL,18,Fsector.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
