OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1773668268
OL,3,CLondoners could be charged for driving
OL,4,CSUVs in the capital
OL,6,F"As the numbers of large SUVs increase
OL,7,Fon London's roads, it is right that
OL,8,FTfL consider their impact on safety
OL,9,Fand how they affect other road users."
OL,11,FProposals to clamp down on the biggest
OL,12,Fvehicles could come later this year.
OL,14,FTransport for London is also poised to
OL,15,Fincrease 20mph zones and cut speed
OL,16,Flimits on its fastest roads from 50mph
OL,17,Fto 40mph to tackle road deaths.
OL,19,FThe Vision Zero Action Plan sets out
OL,20,F43 new actions that aim to create a
OL,21,Fsafer, healthier London.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@fO]
